pullrequest.title: Remove TinyXML symbols from public API: Move uninstalled headers

content.raw: I looked into fixing this. I think the problem, as the error suggests, is that some of the symbols are found in both `libsdformat.so` and the object files created from the sources in `SDF_BUILD_TESTS_EXTRA_EXE_SRCS`. There is an MSVC option `FORCE:MULTIPLE` that seems to work, but it generates a warning. For now, I have disabled the tests in de1a98c.
